Bloggy 

Stay connected from anywhere, community journaling with friends! 
 
Bloggy is a flask app that allows users to register/login, create, edit and delete posts called "Bloggys", view their bloggys and the bloggys of other users,
like bloggys, generate a virtual diary from their bloggys, etc. 
 Notable feature:
 - responsive and color-changing like buttons whose info is remembered even after refreshing the session
 - multi-user interface
 - use of JS 
 - well routed
 - Generating a virtual diary
 - scroll bar

## Installation
- virtual environment
- pipenv install: flask, pymysql, flask-bcrypt, json 
 
